name: Artificial drops. Proliferation #1
description:
Artificial drops. Proliferation #1
Every one of us has already experienced  something like that. Any music is visual.
 
The sound images of the Artificial Drops collection are immersed in the world of music pulsing with drops of paint.

"Artificial drops" is an exploration of sound, movement, color and texture.

All works have unique movements that correspond to the rhythm and sound range.


1280x1280
